1. download LM Studio from https://lmstudio.ai/
2. add zephyr model (zephyr-7b-beta-q4_k_m.gguf) it (can change according to your need) 
3. in the terminal section on local server, and CORS for security

## üöÄ Project Setup

### üêß For macOS/Linux users:

Make sure you have Python 3 installed.

1. Open a terminal.
2. Run:
    ```bash
    make setup
    ```

If you don't have make, you can also run the setup script directly:
$ bash setup.sh

### ü™ü For macOS/Linux users:

# Option 1: Using setup.bat (Recommended)
1. Open Command Prompt (cmd).
2. Navigate to the project directory.
3. Run:
    $ setup.bat

# Option 2: Using PowerShell
1. Open PowerShell.
2. Navigate to the project directory.
3. Run:
    $ .\setup.ps1